      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I'm not surprised to hear that your publisher is pushing for more \"brand consistency.\" It's a common practice in the industry, but I'm concerned that it may stifle the unique voice and creativity that has made your series successful. I'd like to discuss this further with you and explore options for finding a balance between consistency and creative freedom. Can we schedule a meeting to go over the details of the new template and see if there's a way to adapt it to your vision?",
